If you have car sex

509
00:33:45,192 --> 00:33:50,471
one might leave behind
a strand of hair, or an earring.

510
00:33:50,572 --> 00:33:51,681
Right.

511
00:33:51,782 --> 00:33:55,626
But how can you forget
your own panties?

512
00:33:56,161 --> 00:34:00,047
So, true!
It's a hard thing to forget!

513
00:34:01,083 --> 00:34:05,344
So, this raises suspicions
about this woman.

514
00:34:06,380 --> 00:34:07,596
Are you getting this?

515
00:34:17,182 --> 00:34:18,750
Oh my... like meth or cocaine?!

516
00:34:18,851 --> 00:34:20,568
Shhh!
The kids...

517
00:34:21,103 --> 00:34:22,295
What do we do?

518
00:34:22,396 --> 00:34:25,048
What if anyone finds something
like white powder in your car?

519
00:34:25,148 --> 00:34:27,742
Calm down, relax!

520
00:34:28,277 --> 00:34:29,784
Relax.

521
00:34:30,320 --> 00:34:33,621
For now it's just a supposition.
A reasonable suspicion.

522
00:34:34,158 --> 00:34:35,808
But, nothing to call the police about.

523
00:34:35,909 --> 00:34:37,752
Of course, not.

524
00:34:38,328 --> 00:34:44,108
