1280
01:27:49,642 --> 01:27:51,525
Like old dried radish?

1281
01:27:52,144 --> 01:27:53,361
No.

1282
01:27:53,479 --> 01:27:55,713
You know that smell
when you boil a rag?

1283
01:27:55,814 --> 01:27:57,198
