1356
01:37:05,697 --> 01:37:10,459
Honey, sister Chung-sook is

1357
01:37:10,994 --> 01:37:15,810
really a nice person.

1358
01:37:16,917 --> 01:37:20,738
But, she shoved me with her foot.

1359
01:37:22,881 --> 01:37:24,932
Repeat after me.

1360
01:37:25,467 --> 01:37:28,185
Chung-sook.

1361
01:37:29,721 --> 01:37:33,148
Chung-sook.

1362
01:37:42,067 --> 01:37:44,368
Ki-woo!

1363
01:37:45,153 --> 01:37:46,762
What at are you doing over there?

1364
01:37:46,863 --> 01:37:47,963
Huh?

1365
01:38:02,963 --> 01:38:07,099
H. E. L. P. M ...

1366
01:39:12,407 --> 01:39:13,624
