1367
01:39:14,284 --> 01:39:15,584
Huh?

1368
01:39:16,620 --> 01:39:20,339
What is that plan from earlier?

1369
01:39:21,916 --> 01:39:23,926
What are you talking about?

1370
01:39:24,961 --> 01:39:27,679
Earlier, you said you had a plan.

1371
01:39:28,214 --> 01:39:30,182
What are you going to do? There...

1372
01:39:30,759 --> 01:39:32,017
in the basement.

1373
01:39:33,053 --> 01:39:38,774
Ki-woo, you know
what kind of plan never fails?

1374
01:39:40,352 --> 01:39:42,878
A 'Non-Plan.' A non-plan.

1375
01:39:42,979 --> 01:39:44,655
"No plan."

1376
01:39:45,190 --> 01:39:46,740
You know why?

1377
01:39:48,777 --> 01:39:55,457
If you make a plan,
life never turns out that way.

1378
01:39:55,992 --> 01:39:57,501
Look around here.

1379
01:39:58,036 --> 01:40:03,674
You think all these people planned in droves,
"Let's spend the night in a gym"?

1380
01:40:04,209 --> 01:40:06,176
But, look now.

1381
01:40:06,336 --> 01:40:10,347
Everyone's sleeping on the
gym floor, us included.

1382
01:40:11,883 --> 01:40:15,310
That's why people
shouldn't have plans.

1383
01:40:17,347 --> 01:40:21,125
With no plan,
nothing can go wrong.

1384
01:40:21,226 --> 01:40:28,115
If you start out without a plan, even if something
spins out of control, it doesn't matter.

1385
01:40:29,150 --> 01:40:32,119
Whether you kill someone
or betray your country.

1386
01:40:33,655 --> 01:40:37,290
None of it fucking matters.
Got it?

1387
01:40:38,952 --> 01:40:40,419
Father.

1388
01:40:42,455 --> 01:40:44,047
I'm sorry.

1389
01:40:44,666 --> 01:40:46,508
For what, son?

1390
01:40:49,546 --> 01:40:51,179
Everything.

1391
01:40:51,840 --> 01:40:53,640
All of it.

1392
01:40:55,677 --> 01:40:57,978
I'll take the responsibility.

1393
01:40:58,513 --> 01:41:00,731
What are you talking about?

1394
01:41:02,767 --> 01:41:05,360
Why are you embracing
that rock like that?

1395
01:41:05,979 --> 01:41:07,696
This?

1396
01:41:13,236 --> 01:41:16,371
It keeps clinging to me.

1397
01:41:18,408 --> 01:41:22,794
You'd better get some sleep.

1398
01:41:25,832 --> 01:41:27,424
Really!

1399
01:41:28,960 --> 01:41:31,553
