1400
01:41:44,601 --> 01:41:46,460
Teacher Jessica?
Sorry to call on a Sunday morning.

1401
01:41:46,561 --> 01:41:48,921
Are you free for lunch today?

1402
01:41:49,022 --> 01:41:52,783
We're having an impromptu
birthday for Da-song.

1403
01:41:54,360 --> 01:41:56,095
Are you having a birthday party?

1404
01:41:56,196 --> 01:41:59,623
If you come too,
Da-song will be so very happy.

1405
01:41:59,824 --> 01:42:03,960
And have as much pasta, gratin,
and salmon steak as you want.

1406
01:42:04,078 --> 01:42:06,188
People will be here by 1pm
so be here by then.

1407
01:42:06,289 --> 01:42:09,400
And I'll count today
as one of your sessions.

1408
01:42:09,501 --> 01:42:12,052
You know what I mean?
See you later!

1409
01:42:13,296 --> 01:42:14,738
- Mom.
- Yeah?

1410
01:42:14,839 --> 01:42:18,492
For the impromptu birthday
should we invite teacher Kevin too?

1411
01:42:18,593 --> 01:42:21,370
Great idea! Why not?
Will you contact him?

1412
01:42:21,471 --> 01:42:25,374
Get some more sleep! You need to rest.
You had a rough day yesterday.

1413
01:42:25,475 --> 01:42:29,628
If you're doing a party,
won't you need to do the rounds?

1414
01:42:29,729 --> 01:42:34,116
Right, the wine shop,
supermarket, bakery, florist...

1415
01:42:34,943 --> 01:42:37,577
I already told driver Kim to hurry over.

1416
01:42:37,695 --> 01:42:39,388
I'll pay him overtime.

1417
01:42:39,489 --> 01:42:40,589
Perfect!

1418
01:42:51,125 --> 01:42:54,803
Everyone, calm down, calm down!

1419
01:43:02,679 --> 01:43:05,998
In the basement...

1420
01:43:06,099 --> 01:43:08,375
