then arrange them...

1422
01:43:13,022 --> 01:43:16,241
No, come to the window.
I need to show you.

1423
01:43:17,944 --> 01:43:19,720
With Da-song's tent in the middle

1424
01:43:19,821 --> 01:43:23,356
Set the tables outward in a curve...

1425
01:43:23,457 --> 01:43:25,601
A crane-wing formation!

1426
01:43:25,702 --> 01:43:28,987
Like Admiral Yi used. You remember
Battle of The Hansan Island?

1427
01:43:29,088 --> 01:43:31,648
Think of the tent as the
Japanese warship.

1428
01:43:31,749 --> 01:43:37,029
And our tables in the crane-wing formation
in a semi-circular fashion.

1429
01:43:37,130 --> 01:43:41,325
Then near the tent will be the
barbeque grill, firewood and such

1430
01:43:41,426 --> 01:43:43,627
all nicely arranged.

1431
01:43:43,728 --> 01:43:47,589
That will be great!
Bring your husband too!

1432
01:43:47,690 --> 01:43:48,415
Yeah!

1433
01:43:48,516 --> 01:43:52,485
And definitely no presents,
just come!

1434
01:43:53,354 --> 01:43:55,047
Dress code?

1435
01:43:55,148 --> 01:43:58,783
It's just an impromptu.
You can wear sweat pants if you want!

1436
01:43:59,819 --> 01:44:05,582
