my culinary skills.

1438
01:44:08,828 --> 01:44:13,965
Right! Right!
We'll drink wine in daylight.

1439
01:44:15,543 --> 01:44:19,054
If you would sing a song,
that'd be grand ! You know the one...

1440
01:44:35,104 --> 01:44:37,906
Ajumma, shhh!
He's still sleeping!

1441
01:44:38,441 --> 01:44:41,510
Today the sky's so blue,
and no yellow-dust pollution!

1442
01:44:41,611 --> 01:44:43,787
Thanks to all the rain yesterday.

1443
01:44:44,822 --> 01:44:46,056
Right.

1444
01:44:46,157 --> 01:44:50,252
So we traded camping
for a garden party. Deal!

1445
01:44:51,287 --> 01:44:53,088
It's lemons into lemonade.

1446
01:44:56,209 --> 01:45:01,263
Right, what would we have done
