01:45:07,845 --> 01:45:11,731
Right, you've got the Mini Cooper so,
we'll just squeeze it into our garage.

1449
01:45:12,000 --> 01:45:13,000
Go on up!

1450
01:45:13,101 --> 01:45:18,013
Back it in tight.
Just don't block the Benz.

1451
01:45:18,114 --> 01:45:21,214
You're here!
It's been so long!

1452
01:45:24,237 --> 01:45:26,579
