1453
01:45:44,632 --> 01:45:46,766
Oppa, you were thinking
of something else.

1454
01:45:46,926 --> 01:45:48,310
What?

1455
01:45:49,345 --> 01:45:52,522
While we were kissing, you were
thinking of something else.

1456
01:45:54,642 --> 01:45:55,900
No.

1457
01:45:56,936 --> 01:46:00,572
What do you mean, no?
You're still doing it.

1458
01:46:03,109 --> 01:46:04,367
Wow.

1459
01:46:05,987 --> 01:46:08,705
Everyone looks great, right?

1460
01:46:10,116 --> 01:46:13,877
Even for an impromptu,
they all look so cool

1461
01:46:14,746 --> 01:46:17,130
and so natural.

1462
01:46:19,167 --> 01:46:20,425
Da-hye.

1463
01:46:23,004 --> 01:46:24,637
Do I fit in well?

1464
01:46:26,015 --> 01:46:27,741
What?

1465
01:46:28,676 --> 01:46:31,686
Do I fit in well here?

1466
01:46:41,606 --> 01:46:43,823
