I can't do anything about it.

1477
01:47:20,061 --> 01:47:21,628
But the concept is simple.

1478
01:47:21,729 --> 01:47:27,050
Teacher Jessica will carry out
the birthday cake in a little parade.

1479
01:47:27,151 --> 01:47:31,138
Then, we jump out
and attack teacher Jessica

1480
01:47:31,239 --> 01:47:33,473
swinging our Indian tomahawks!

1481
01:47:33,574 --> 01:47:34,349
Ah, right.

1482
01:47:34,450 --> 01:47:39,879
